(Abstract of Decision.)

O’Connor, J., dissenting.

Heard in first division, first district, this court at October term, 1939;opinion filed May 20, 1940.Schnackenberg, Hansen & Towle and Harry I. Weisbrod, for appellant; Elmer J. Schnackenberg, of counsel; Nash, Ahern, McDermott, McNally & Kiley, for certain appellee; Richard F. Shay and John J. Kennelly, of counsel; Maurice L. Davis, for certain other appellee; Maurice L.
